    <string name="kiosk_pinning_hint">This tablet isn\'t fully locked down yet. The app returns to the giving screen whenever someone leaves it and reopens on boot, but without one-time device-owner setup Android still lets a determined person briefly reach the notification shade or settings — that can\'t be fully blocked. To make the kiosk truly un-leavable (notification shade off, no exit without the PIN), set this app as the default Home app and follow the device-owner steps in docs/TABLET_SETUP.md.</string>
